---
// AboutDoctor.astro
// Alternating dark canvas section (bg-surface-tile-1, text white) for clinical authority and warmth
---

<section id="doctor" class="w-full bg-[#272729] text-white py-20 border-b border-white/5">
  <div class="max-w-[1068px] mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-center">
      
      <!-- Left Column: Portrait resting on surface -->
      <div class="col-span-1 md:col-span-5 flex justify-center reveal">
        <div class="relative w-full max-w-[360px] aspect-[4/5] rounded-[18px] overflow-hidden border border-white/10 shadow-[0_20px_40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.3)] group bg-[#2a2a2c]">
          <img 
            src="/images/doctor.png" 
            alt="Dr. Harish Mansuri BDS MDS - Principal Dentist at Dental Clinic World Dental Studio" 
            class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale-[15%] group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-500 scale-100 group-hover:scale-103"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/60 via-transparent to-transparent"></div>
          <div class="absolute bottom-6 left-6 right-6">
            <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-primary-on-dark uppercase tracking-wider mb-1 block">Clinical Chief</span>
            <p class="font-display font-semibold text-xl tracking-tight">Dr. Harish Mansuri, MDS</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right Column: Professional profile & philosophy -->
      <div class="col-span-1 md:col-span-7 flex flex-col justify-center reveal delay-150">
        <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-primary-on-dark uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Meet the Doctor</span>
        <h2 class="font-display font-semibold text-3xl sm:text-4xl leading-tight tracking-tight mb-6">
          Dr. Harish Mansuri <br class="hidden sm:inline" />
          <span class="text-primary-on-dark">BDS, MDS (Prosthodontist & Implantologist)</span>
        </h2>
        
        <p class="text-[15px] text-neutral-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Dr. Harish Mansuri is a highly recognized Prosthodontist and Oral Implantologist with over 15 years of clinical expertise. He completed his Masters of Dental Surgery (MDS) from one of India's premier government dental institutions, specializing in advanced smile styling, implant placement, and full-mouth dental rehabilitations.
        </p>

        <p class="text-[15px] text-neutral-300 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          Recognized for his gentle treatment style and absolute transparency, Dr. Sharma ensures patients understand every step of their treatment beforehand. Under his leadership, Dental Clinic World Dental Studio follows stringent international sterilizing procedures to provide a 100% safe, pain-free environment.
        </p>

        <!-- Quote block matching premium style -->
        <div class="border-l-2 border-primary-on-dark pl-6 py-2 mb-8 bg-white/3 rounded-r-md">
          <blockquote class="text-base italic text-neutral-200 font-sans tracking-tight mb-2">
            "Clinical dentistry is not just about solving dental disease. It is about restoring confidence, relieving pain with empathy, and making sure patients walk out with a natural, healthy smile."
          </blockquote>
          <cite class="text-xs font-semibold text-primary-on-dark uppercase tracking-wider">— Dr. Harish Mansuri</cite>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 items-center">
          <span class="text-xs font-medium text-neutral-400 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-full px-4 py-1.5">IDA Member</span>
          <span class="text-xs font-medium text-neutral-400 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-full px-4 py-1.5">ITI (International Team for Implantology)</span>
          <span class="text-xs font-medium text-neutral-400 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-full px-4 py-1.5">FICOI (USA)</span>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

